criteria.driver_alignment:
Discover — defined the assignment requirement to produce base/upside/downside scenarios and required sensitivity tests;  
Represent — mapped which assumptions (store growth, margins, WACC, terminal growth, synergy capture) feed each scenario;  
Implement — built scenario dictionaries and modular code to run multi‑scenario DCF, comps, and synergy pro‑forma;  
Validate — ran sensitivity sweeps and inspected how changes in assumptions (WACC, terminal growth, synergy capture) produced monotonic, interpretable valuation changes.
